    `SiteMap` is a class which contains a grid of `SquareType` (siteMap). siteMap is a two dimensional array of SquareType where siteMap[0][0] is the top left corner, where x = 0, y = 0 respectively. A site map text file, that is found on the classpath can be used to initialise the grid. This class has the ability to display the siteMap and update the squares as they are cleared. This class provides access to each of the SquareType locations on the siteMap grid.
